<item>
            <title>[BATCH-917] Concurrent modification of execution context in tasklet step</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/BATCH-917</link>
                <project id="10090" key="BATCH">Spring Batch</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Concurrent modification of execution context in tasklet step.  &lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=63162&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=63162&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The tasklet step is making a false assumption about execution context updates (it just clears the dirty flag once per chunk, but there is no reason chunks need to be serial).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
